Name of person(s) with parental responsibility.

The practice will expect full co-operation in the supply of these details from the parent / carer, otherwise registration will be refused. The health visitor will be informed within 5 days of registration of all children under 16 who register with the practice, including temporary registrations.

Staff should be vigilant in the instance of multiple short-term temporary registrations for the same child, especially if consecutive. In the event of concern the permanent GP should be contacted.

